    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the sophisticated buyer. It delivers a refined driving experience, characterized by consistent performance and a well-preserved interior. Rigorously inspected to ensure operational excellence, this motorcar offers a seamless fusion of longevity and prestige. We invite you to experience a vehicle that remains in commendable form, ready for immediate acquisition.",
      "price": 34800.0,
