    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid condition and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. It's been well-loved and taken care of, so it's totally ready to hit the road with a new owner today! It drives like a dream and still looks sharp. If you're looking for a dependable car that's ready for its next adventure, this is the one. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. This high-revving engine utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a speed-sensitive M Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including professional reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The chassis retains its signature balance with MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup, offering precise turn-in and exceptional mid-corner stability. This is a driver-spec example that prioritizes mechanical integrity and performance over concours-level aesthetics.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Clean title. Regular maintenance performed. Runs well. Minor cosmetic wear.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive condition, offering a perfect balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, with only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary; the leather seats have been regularly treated to prevent cracking, and every button, dial, and digital display functions exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. Mechanically, this car is rock solid. I have maintained a comprehensive folder of service records, including recent oil services, a brake pad replacement, and a cooling system flush. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains tight and responsive. It sits on a set of premium tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a turnkey opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality vehicle that has been treated with the utmost respect.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive engineering, this vehicle has been curated for the discerning driver who prioritizes both performance and prestige. Meticulously maintained and showing clear pride of ownership, it offers a seamless driving experience underpinned by rigorous mechanical standards. The exterior and interior appointments remain in commendable order, reflecting a history of consistent care. This is an exceptional opportunity to secure a high-caliber asset that balances sophisticated styling with proven reliability.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s looking for a new home! It\u2019s been super reliable and is still in great shape for all your daily cruises or weekend getaways. It\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of, so you\u2019re getting a solid car that\u2019s ready to hit the road immediately. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're gonna love how it handles!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
