      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the iconic S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, an engine celebrated for its 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with the M-DCT 7-speed dual-clutch transmission, providing rapid-fire shifts and seamless power delivery to the rear wheels via the M-variable differential lock. The chassis is well-sorted, featuring Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adjustable suspension geometry. Maintenance is up to date, notably including preventative rod bearing replacement and regular fluid intervals for the high-pressure VANOS system. While the exterior shows minor road rash typical of spirited use, the structural integrity and powertrain performance remain top-tier. The interior leather retains excellent tactile feel with only light wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster.",
      "price": 34500.0,
